ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of JOANNE WHITTLE of Carleton Place, Ontario, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of H. Glenn Rainbird, O.C.
